# GeminiClaw Dashboard - Environment Variables

# The secret token used to authenticate with the Gateway# [CRITICAL SECURITY WARNING]
# Any variable starting with VITE_ is EMBEDDED in the public Javascript bundle.
# This secret will be VISIBLE to anyone who can load the dashboard in their browser.
# DO NOT expose the dashboard publicly if you use this feature.
VITE_DASHBOARD_SECRET=
# In Vite, variables must start with VITE_ to be exposed to the browser.
VITE_DASHBOARD_SECRET=your_secret_token_here
